Package entity

Class ResourceNodeEntity

java.lang.Object
entity.ResourceNodeEntity
@Entity public class ResourceNodeEntity extends Object
Entity class representing a resource node within a country. A resource node establishes a relationship between a CountryEntity and a ResourceEntity, defining details about the quantity, tier, base capacity, and base production cost for the resource in the country. This entity is mapped to the "resource_node" table and uses a composite key defined by ResourceNodeEntityId.
